quran[26{c,v,t}:
37,77,aur isi ki nasal ko baqi rakha
37,78,aur baad ki naslon mein is ki tareef o tauseef chore di
37,79,salam hai Nooh par tamam duniya walon mein
37,80,hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza diya karte hain
37,81,Dur haqeeqat woh hamaray momin bundon mein se tha
37,82,phir dosray giroh ko hum ne ghark kar diya
37,83,aur Nooh hi ke tareeqay par chalne wala ibrahim tha
37,84,jab woh apne rab ke huzoor qalb Saleem le kar aaya
37,85,"jab uss ne apne baap aur apni qoum se kaha"" yeh kya cheeze hain jin ki tum ibadat kar rahay ho ?"
37,86,kya Allah ko chore kar jhoot gharrey hue mabood chahtay ho ?
37,87,"aakhir Allah Rab alaalmin ke baray mein tumhara kya gumaan hai? """
37,88,phir is ne taron par aik nigah daali
37,89,aur kaha meri tabiyat kharab hai
37,90,chunancha woh log usay chore kar chalay gay
37,91,"unn ke peechay woh chupkay se unn ke mabodon ke mandir mein ghis gaya aur bola"" aap log khatay kyun nahi hain ?"
37,92,"kya ho gaya, aap log boltay bhi nahi? """
37,93,is ke baad woh unn par pal para aur seedhay haath se khoob zrbin lagayen
37,94,( wapas aa kar ) woh log bhage bhage is ke paas aeye
37,95,"is ne kaha"" kya tum apni hi tarashi hui cheezon ko pujte ho ?"
37,96,"halaank Allah hi ne tum ko bhi peda kya hai aur unn cheezon ko bhi jinhein tum banatay ho """
37,97,"unhon ne aapas mein kaha"" is ke liye aik alaao tayyar karo aur usay dehakti hui aag ke dhair mein pheink do """
37,98,"unhon ne is ke khilaaf aik karwai karni chahi thi, magar hum ne unhi ko neecha dikha diya"
37,99,"ibrahim ne kaha"" mein apne rab ki taraf jata hon, wohi meri rahnumai kere ga"
37,100,"ae parwar-digaar, mujhe aik beta ataa kar jo salhonmein se ho """
37,101,( is dua ke jawab mein ) hum ne is ko aik Haleem ( Burdbar ) larke ki basharat di
37,102,"woh larka jab is ke sath daud dhoop karne ki Umar ko poanch gaya to ( aik roz ) ibrahim ne is se kaha,"" beta, mein khawab mein daikhta hon ke mein tujhe zibah kar raha hon, ab to bta, tera kya khayaal hai ?"" uss ne kaha,"" abba jaan, jo kuch aap ko hukum diya ja raha hai usay kar dalie, aap Insha Allah mujhe sabroo-n mein se payen ge """
